OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773666672
OL,3,CDrugs worth #446k seized in police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FAlmost a hundred people have been
OL,7,Farrested across the South West as
OL,8,Fpolice forces crack down on county
OL,9,Flines drug dealing.
OL,11,FOperation Scorpion, which ran last
OL,12,Fweek, also saw #446,000 worth of drugs
OL,13,Fseized, as well as weapons and cash.
OL,15,FThe operation, which ran alongside the
OL,16,Fnational County Lines Intensification
OL,17,FWeek, brought together five South West
OL,18,Fpolice forces; Avon and Somerset,
OL,19,FDorset, Devon and Cornwall,
OL,20,FGloucestershire and Wiltshire.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
