OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773666672
OL,3,CDrugs worth #446k seized in police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FThe majority of the drugs seized in
OL,7,Fthe South West during the week of
OL,8,Faction was in Wiltshire, where
OL,9,F#380,000 worth of drugs were found.
OL,11,FOfficers also visited more than 50 so-
OL,12,Fcalled cuckooed addresses in the
OL,13,Fcounty, where criminals take over
OL,14,Fsomeone's home to use it as a base.
OL,15,FWiltshire Police also arrested 26
OL,16,Fpeople, and seized 10 weapons.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773666672
OL,3,CDrugs worth #446k seized in police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Liz Coles
OL,7,Ffrom Wiltshire Police said: "Our
OL,8,Fmission is clear: keeping Wiltshire
OL,9,Fsafe by removing harmful drugs,
OL,10,Ftargeting suppliers, and disrupting
OL,11,Fcounty lines networks.
OL,13,F"Protecting vulnerable
OL,14,Fpeople`especially children and young
OL,15,Fadults exploited by these
OL,16,Fgangs`remains at the heart of our
OL,17,Fwork. When children go missing, their
OL,18,Frisk increases, and close partnership
OL,19,Fworking is vital to keeping them safe.
OL,26,@oD@]OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773666672
OL,3,CDrugs worth #446k seized in police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,F"We see the harm this criminality
OL,7,Fbrings to our towns and villages. This
OL,8,Fwork doesn't end with one week of
OL,9,Faction, we will continue to take a
OL,10,Frobust, proactive approach.
OL,12,F"Our message is simple: Wiltshire and
OL,13,Fthe South West is no place for drugs.
OL,14,FWe all have a role in raising
OL,15,Fawareness, reporting concerns, and
OL,16,Fpreventing harm."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
