OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773666672
OL,3,CDrugs worth #446k seized in police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FWiltshire Police also worked with
OL,7,FPolice Cadets as part of Hotel Watch,
OL,8,Fin a bid to raise awareness among
OL,9,Fhotel staff of how to spot signs of
OL,10,Fexploitation, including child sexual
OL,11,Fexploitation. Of the 26 hotels
OL,12,Fvisited, 11 failed the checks.
OL,14,FPolice and Crime Commissioner Philip
OL,15,FWilkinson said: "This phase of
OL,16,FOperation Scorpion shows the real
OL,17,Fimpact of a coordinated South West
OL,18,Fapproach, which Wiltshire has led on
OL,19,Ffor this iteration.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
