OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773666672
OL,3,CDrugs worth #446k seized in police
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,F"Our focus on Class A drug supply and
OL,7,Fvulnerable missing children has
OL,8,Fdelivered some strong results and
OL,9,Fvital safeguarding.
OL,11,F"We will continue strengthening our
OL,12,Fpartnerships with schools, local
OL,13,Fservices and community organisations
OL,14,Fto ensure young people are supported
OL,15,Fearly, informed about the risks of
OL,16,Fexploitation, and equipped to seek
OL,17,Fhelp when they need it."
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@XO]
